The global aluminium piston market is projected to witness significant growth during the forecast period 2022-2029. The market is segmented based on type, coating type, vehicle type, sales channel, and region. The type segment is further divided into standard duty and heavy-duty aluminium pistons. In terms of coating type, the market is categorized into dry film lubricants and oil shedding films. Based on vehicle type, the market is segmented into passenger cars, light commercial vehicles, and heavy commercial vehicles. The sales channel segment consists of OEM (Original Equipment Manufacturer) and aftermarket channels. Geographically, the market is analyzed across North America, Europe, Asia-Pacific, Middle East and Africa, and South America.

